Then system_components colon.
Indent infrastructure colon dash EKS Cluster financial-rag-prod,
dash RDS PostgreSQL with pgvector,
dash ElastiCache Redis,
dash S3 buckets for backups,
dash ECR repositories.

55
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:50,000
Indent application colon dash FastAPI application as api service,
dash Agent workers as agent service,
dash Ingestion cron jobs,
dash Helm charts.

56
00:02:50,000 --> 00:03:20,000
Indent observability colon dash Prometheus metrics,
dash Loki logs,
dash Tempo traces,
dash Grafana dashboards.

57
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:50,000
Indent security colon dash Vault for secrets,
dash Cilium network policies,
dash Falco runtime security,
dash OPA forward slash Gatekeeper policies.

58
00:03:50,000 --> 00:04:20,000
Then excluded_components colon.
Dash Developer workstations out of scope,
dash Customer on-premises environments,
dash Third-party APIs like OpenAI and Groq with note that vendor assessment covers,
dash Public internet infrastructure.

59
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:50,000
Then data_flows colon.
First flow. source colon SEC EDGAR API.
destination colon Ingestion cron job.
data_type colon Public filings.
classification colon Public.

60
00:04:50,000 --> 00:05:20,000
Second flow. source colon User via API.
destination colon API service.
data_type colon Query text comma API keys.
classification colon Confidential.

61
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:50,000
Third flow. source colon API service.
destination colon OpenAI forward slash Groq API.
data_type colon Query context.
classification colon Confidential.
Close the file.

62
