CC6.6 colon Encryption of data at rest.
CC6.7 colon Encryption of data in transit.

86
00:02:30,000 --> 00:03:00,000
Then a comment for CC7.0 System Operations.
CC7.1 colon System availability.
CC7.2 colon Monitoring and alerting.
CC7.4 colon Backup and recovery.
CC7.5 colon Incident response.

87
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:30,000
Comment for CC8.0 Change Management.
CC8.1 colon Change management procedures.
Comment for CC9.0 Risk Mitigation.
CC9.2 colon Vendor risk management.

88
00:03:30,000 --> 00:04:00,000
Then selected_controls colon.
Each control gets an entry.

89
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:30,000
First control. control_id colon CC6.1.
title colon Logical access security.
implementation colon API key authentication comma RBAC.
evidence colon Kubernetes RBAC configs comma API logs.
owner colon at sign security dash team.

90
00:04:30,000 --> 00:05:00,000
Second control. control_id colon CC6.6.
title colon Encryption at rest.
implementation colon RDS encryption comma S3 SSE-KMS.
evidence colon AWS Config rules comma KMS key policies.
owner colon at sign platform dash team.

91
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:30,000
Third control. control_id colon CC6.7.
title colon Encryption in transit.
implementation colon TLS one point three comma Cilium mTLS.
evidence colon Ingress TLS config comma certificates.
owner colon at sign platform dash team.

92
00:05:30,000 --> 00:06:00,000
Fourth control. control_id colon CC7.1.
title colon System availability.
implementation colon Multi-AZ comma HPA comma PDBs.
evidence colon SLO dashboards comma uptime reports.
owner colon at sign platform dash team.

93
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:30,000
Fifth control. control_id colon CC7.2.
title colon Monitoring and alerting.
implementation colon Prometheus comma Loki comma PagerDuty.
evidence colon Alert configs comma on-call schedules.
owner colon at sign platform dash team.

94
00:06:30,000 --> 00:07:00,000
Sixth control. control_id colon CC7.4.
title colon Backup and recovery.
implementation colon Velero comma RDS backups.
evidence colon Backup logs comma restore tests.
owner colon at sign platform dash team.

95
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:30,000
Seventh control. control_id colon CC8.1.
title colon Change management.
implementation colon GitOps comma PR reviews.
evidence colon PR approvals comma ArgoCD logs.
owner colon at sign eng dash team.

96
00:07:30,000 --> 00:08:00,000
Eighth control. control_id colon CC9.2.
title colon Vendor risk management.
implementation colon Vendor assessments.
evidence colon Vendor questionnaires comma BAAs.
owner colon at sign compliance dash team.

97
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:30,000
Now let me show you how each control maps to actual code.
This is what makes your SOC 2 program real.
Not just documents, but implemented controls.

98
00:08:30,000 --> 00:09:00,000
For CC6.6, encryption at rest.
In terraform forward slash rds-encryption dot tf.
The aws_db_instance resource for financial_rag has storage_encrypted set to true.
And kms_key_id referencing aws_kms_key.rds_key.arn.

99
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:30,000
