227
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:30,000
The final step before your audit is assembling the evidence package.
This is what you will upload to your auditor's portal.
It needs to be complete, organized, and clearly labeled.

228
00:00:30,000 --> 00:01:00,000
Let me show you the exact structure.

229
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:30,000
soc2-evidence forward slash YYYY-MM-DD.
Inside that, a controls folder.
With files CC6.1-api-keys dot json.
CC6.6-encryption dot json.
CC6.7-tls-cert dot json.

230
00:01:30,000 --> 00:02:00,000
CC7.1-uptime dot json.
CC7.2-alerts dot json.
