CC8.1-changes dot json.
And CC9.2-vendors dot json.

231
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:30,000
A policies folder with security-policy dot pdf.
incident-response dot pdf.
change-management dot pdf.
and vendor-management dot pdf.

232
00:02:30,000 --> 00:03:00,000
A runbooks folder with incident-response dot md.
backup-restore dot md.
and on-call dot md.
And a README dot md.

233
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:30,000
Now create the assembly script.
In scripts forward slash assemble-evidence dot sh.

234
00:03:30,000 --> 00:04:00,000
Set DATE to today's date.
